cast.overview: Just when Charlie is feeling especially frustrated by the lack of excitement in her small town in California, she receives wonderful news: Her uncle and namesake, Charlie, is coming to visit. However, as secrets about him come to the fore, her admiration turns into suspicion.
cast.title: Shadow of a Doubt

details.biography: A stage actress, Urecal made her screen debut in 1934. For the remainder  of her career and two hundred plus movies, she played cleaning women,  landladies, shopkeepers and the like. She was known as a Marjorie Main  type actress and later went on to a career in television playing in such  shows as "Tugboat Annie" and "Peter Gunn." Minerva claimed her name was  an amalgam of her hometown, Eureka, California.
details.name: Minerva Urecal
